OL,3,CWhy climate change is pushing up the
OL,4,Ccost of chocolate Easter eggs
OL,6,FThe Energy and Climate Intelligence
OL,7,FUnit (ECIU), an environmental non-
OL,8,Fprofit, has set out how the
OL,9,Fcombination of climate change and El
OL,10,FNino conditions have contributed to
OL,11,Fdriving up cocoa prices ahead of the
OL,12,Fchocolate-heavy holiday on Sunday
OL,13,FMarch 31.
OL,15,FA record price high of more than
OL,16,F$8,200 (#6,500) for cocoa beans was
OL,17,Freached this week - up from $2,600
OL,18,F(#2,000) compared to this time last
OL,19,Fyear.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/10
