OL,3,CWhy climate change is pushing up the
OL,4,Ccost of chocolate Easter eggs
OL,6,FThe development comes as the world's
OL,7,Flargest cocoa exporters - Ivory Coast
OL,8,Fand Ghana - have been hit by extreme
OL,9,Fweather in recent months.
OL,11,FAnalysis from the World Weather
OL,12,FAttribution, which was released on
OL,13,FThursday, showed that climate change
OL,14,Fmade the February heatwave in West
OL,15,FAfrica ten times more likely.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/10
