OL,3,CWhy climate change is pushing up the
OL,4,Ccost of chocolate Easter eggs
OL,6,FIvory Coast and Ghana saw heavy rains
OL,7,Fin December 2023, with total
OL,8,Fprecipitation more than double the 30-
OL,9,Fyear average for the time of year,
OL,10,Fwhich affected yields because of
OL,11,Fissues such as cocoa plants rotting
OL,12,Fwith black pod disease.
OL,14,FThe wet conditions were then followed
OL,15,Fby droughts typical of El Nino
OL,16,Fconditions in February, which further
OL,17,Fdecimated yields due to cocoa being a
OL,18,Fdrought-sensitive crop, the ECIU said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/10
