OL,3,CWhy climate change is pushing up the
OL,4,Ccost of chocolate Easter eggs
OL,6,FEl Nino, a cyclical natural phenomenon
OL,7,Fin the tropical eastern Pacific which
OL,8,Fbrings heat to the surface, can add an
OL,9,Fextra warming effect to the atmosphere
OL,10,Fand oceans on top of that from global
OL,11,Fgreenhouse gas emissions, which
OL,12,Fcontinue to rise.
