OL,3,CWhy climate change is pushing up the
OL,4,Ccost of chocolate Easter eggs
OL,6,FIn a report released on Thursday, the
OL,7,FECIU noted that the impacts of this
OL,8,Fvolatile weather "has fed through to
OL,9,Finternational commodity prices".
OL,11,FAlmost all cocoa globally - 99.9% - is
OL,12,Fgrown in countries that are the most
OL,13,Fvulnerable and least well prepared to
OL,14,Fcope with worsening climate impacts,
OL,15,Fthe ECIU said, citing data from the
OL,16,FUnited Nations (UN) Food and
OL,17,FAgriculture Organisation.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/10
