OL,3,CWhy climate change is pushing up the
OL,4,Ccost of chocolate Easter eggs
OL,6,FThe paper also synthesised UK
OL,7,Fgovernment trade data and University
OL,8,Fof Notre Dame's Global Adaptation
OL,9,FIndex, finding that 58 million
OL,10,Fkilograms of cocoa beans worth #127
OL,11,Fmillion were imported to the UK
OL,12,Fdirectly from these countries, with
OL,13,F85% of all the UK's cocoa beans coming
OL,14,Ffrom the Ivory Coast alone.
OL,16,FAmber Sawyer, an ECIU analyst, said
OL,17,Ffarmers will need more support to
OL,18,Fprotect their livelihoods and to keep
OL,19,Fthe flow of cocoa beans - as well as
OL,20,Fother commodities like tea, bananas
OL,21,Fand rice - coming to the UK.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/10
