OL,3,CWhy climate change is pushing up the
OL,4,Ccost of chocolate Easter eggs
OL,6,F"Farmers in West Africa who grow the
OL,7,Fmain ingredient, cocoa beans, of the
OL,8,FEaster eggs many of us are looking
OL,9,Fforward to are struggling in the face
OL,10,Fof both extreme heat and extremes in
OL,11,Frainfall," she said.
OL,13,F"Wealthy nations like the UK can
OL,14,Fprovide financial and technical
OL,15,Fsupport to developing countries to
OL,16,Fhelp their farmers better cope with
OL,17,Fthese extremes.
OL,19,F"Ultimately, if we're to stop these
OL,20,Fextremes getting ever worse, we have
OL,21,Fto reach net zero emissions."
