OL,3,CWhy climate change is pushing up the
OL,4,Ccost of chocolate Easter eggs
OL,6,FJon Walker, Fairtrade's senior advisor
OL,7,Ffor cocoa, said: "While high prices
OL,8,Fmay seem like a windfall for farmers,
OL,9,Fonce they eventually filter through to
OL,10,Fthe farmgate, the underlying causes
OL,11,Fare worrying.
OL,13,F"Higher prices offset by lower
OL,14,Fproductivity simply perpetuates the
OL,15,Fincome insecurity that keeps farmers
OL,16,Ftrapped in poverty and threatens the
OL,17,Ffuture of cocoa.
OL,19,F"It remains to be seen if supply will
OL,20,Fbounce back, or whether the current
OL,21,Ftrend will be longer-lasting.
